{"tid":808273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金融風暴2.0】151隻港股創52周新低 騰訊、滙控走唔甩","createTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b80303b3c78a84657c408ab82a47bde01b3f7e","tid":808273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180906/large/1536213127_30c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180906%2Flarge%2F1536213127_30c7.jpg&h=9b6fe736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港股現跌308點，報26,935點，只差不足100點便創下52周新低。<br />\n<br />\n股份當中，今日共有151隻股份創下52周新低，除騰訊（700）外，還包括滙控（005）、國壽（2628）、中行（3988）、恒地（012）<br />\n<br />\n至於創52周新高的股份，只有4隻，包括昆侖能源（135）、微創醫療（853）及兩隻創業板股份。"}]}